title: Gameboy&GBC for PS2 With Roms
description:
This is a Gameboy and Gameboy color Emulator for that Runs on The Playstation 2 platform	
All the roms are provided it is already esr patched if you already 
have freemcboot installed then just burn this and enjoy.

this iso is designed to run on an american (NTSC) console if you
Live in an NTSC region just burn to a DVD-R and enjoy. -R dvd's Work
 Better with game consoles than +R DVD's  


For PAL Users Ive included A Quick Easy Solution with instructions.
